foods.ingredients: BONELESS, SKINLESS CHICKEN BREAST FILLETS CONTAINING UP TO 32% OF A SOLUTION OF: TERIYAKI SAUCE [WATER, SOY SAUCE (WATER, SOYBEANS, WHEAT, SALT, LACTIC ACID, SODIUM BENZOATE), SUGAR, BROWN SUGAR, GARLIC, HONEY, MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SPICES, SESAME OIL, CONTAINS 2 PERCENT OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: CARAMEL (COLOR), GARLIC CHILI SAUCE (SALTED CHILI PEPPER, GARLIC, SUGAR, RICE VINEGAR, WATER, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, ACETIC ACID), GARLIC POWDER, NATURAL FLAVORS, ONION POWDER, POTASSIUM CHLORIDE, SALT, SORBIC ACID (PRESERVATIVE), SOYBEANS, VINEGAR, XANTHAN GUM], WATER, VINEGAR, SALT, SEASONING [GUM ARABIC, CHICKEN BROTH POWDER, YEAST EXTRACT, SALT, NATURAL FLAVORS (INCLUDING SMOKE FLAVOR), SUNFLOWER OIL, VEGETABLE STOCK (CARROT, ONION, CELERY), MALTODEXTRIN, VEGETABLE EXTRACT (MOLASSES)].
